    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Sports is very well and they making many athelete and acheivers many achievements by the players",
          "name": "Lalithavarshini",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College will provide lots of inside and outside campus competitions to enhance the students talents.",
          "name": "Mahalakshmi S",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Speaking of curriculum is updated and includes all the necessary developments in the field.",
          "name": "Janarthani M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Green spaces around the campus add to the aesthetic appeal",
          "name": "Janarthani M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library is massive and offers a quiet study environment",
          "name": "Janarthani M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the college environment which is greenery ,the infrastructure of this college is constructed before 70 years withthe oldest method",
          "name": "MEJORA R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are so many schemes for poor students like manna scheme then helping for those students to pay their fees.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are so many cultural program conducted by the faculty.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the atmosphere. They always keep the campus clean. There are so many rain water harvesting tank. There are more than 1000 trees with biological name stick on those.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I think my college is very good college and i liked the fatima college. And most people of liked the college.",
          "name": "Fathima Rosy",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Dress code is followed strictly by the management",
          "name": "sathya sheela",
          "course_tag_name": "MBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Rules and regulations are followed strictly.",
          "name": "sathya sheela",
          "course_tag_name": "MBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "They were very stright in function times, we couldn't be free",
          "name": "swetha",
          "course_tag_name": "BAJMC"
        },
        {
          "text": "Discipline committee the staffs are favour for them",
          "name": "Lalithavarshini",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College starts at 8.30 You should be at college before 8.15 if you're late you have to go to library and do cleaning work and send  you after 2hours and you marked as absent",
          "name": "Lalithavarshini",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Water facilities are there but still need more in count.",
          "name": "Mahalakshmi S",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel is very strict, so that if someone goes late to eat because of some valid reason, they will be scolded  by the workers",
          "name": "Janarthani M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "They not allow us to enjoy the cultural program by dancing nd shouting.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Dress code is most but there they put strict dress code that is not based on this generation.",
